g.text: WHERE phone = ? AND sms_code = ? AND expires_at > NOW()
INSERT INTO users (phone, name, is_verified, created_at)
SELECT lc.*, u.* FROM login_codes lc
JOIN users u ON lc.user_id = u.id
WHERE u.phone = ? AND lc.code = ? AND lc.expires_at > NOW()
